  "title": "FINANCE EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>CONTRACT JOBS!</p><p>6 -12 months Contract</p><p>(with possibility of extension)</p><h2><strong>FINANCE EXECUTIVE</strong></h2><p>SINGAPOREANS/ PRs ONLY</p><p><strong>($3,300.00 - $4,400.00)</strong></p><p><br /><u><strong>LOCATION</strong></u></p><p><strong>Delta / Clementi / Kent Ridge</strong></p><p><u><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>Payroll & Financial Support</strong></u></p><ul><li>Process monthly payroll accurately, including salary adjustments, bonuses, allowances deductions, and final payments</li><li>Work closely with HR on system updates and on final salary payments</li><li>Handle payroll and manpower expense inquiries from employees and stakeholders</li><li>Administer the e-claim system and maintain approval matrices</li><li>Reconcile payroll-relating to payroll, tax, and employee claims</li><li>Perform other payroll and administrative duties as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Controls and Compliance</strong></u></p><ul><li>Ensure payroll controls operate effectively and accurately</li><li>Review payroll processes, identify weaknesses, and implement corrective actions</li><li>Management payroll suspense accounts and ensure timely clearance</li><li>Ensure compliance with CPF Act, Income Tax Act, and internal policies</li></ul><p><u><strong>Productivity & Process improvement</strong></u></p><ul><li>Support digitisation of payroll and financial processing</li><li>Undertake adhoc projects and assignments too improve efficiency</li></ul><p><u><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma / degree or its equivalent.</li><li>3 or 5 years of working experience in payroll, and experience with the SAP payroll system would be an advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of Singapore Statutory laws (CPF Act, Income Tax Act)</li><li>MS Office, Excel</li><li>Organized and meticulous in handling numbers and data.</li><li>A team player with a positive working attitude who is willing to learn and adapt.</li><li>Experience in SAP would be an added advantage.</li><li>Able to adhere to timelines.</li></ul><p><u><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></u></p><ul><li>Official Hours                     </li><li>Monday to Thursday: 8.30am – 6.00pm, Friday: 8.30am – 5.30pm </li><li>Lunch hour (60 mins) Service is not required on Saturdays, Sundays, and gazetted public holidays.</li></ul><p><strong>SERVICE CONNECTIONS HR CONSULTANCY PTE LTD</strong></p><h2>Email resume to - <a href=\"mailto:servcon@singnet.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">servcon@singnet.com.sg</a><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></h2><p>Call for more details please call at 6333 0052</p><p>Mondays to Fridays</p><p>9.00am - 5.00pm</p><p>111 North Bridge Road #07-30Peninsula Plaza Singapore 179098<br /><a href=\"http://www.serviceconnections.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.serviceconnections.com.sg</a></p><p>License no: 09C4937 / R11022931</p>",
